- Requirements:
   sbcl, g++, make, git

- Download compiler and virtual machine:
   git clone http://github.com/flavioc/cl-meld (compiler)
   git clone http://github.com/flavioc/meld (virtual machine)

- Install compiler

   $ cd cl-meld/scripts
# Will install quicklisp and all required packages
   $ bash standalone.sh
# Move quick lisp to home directory
   $ mv compile ~/quicklisp
# Install compiler scripts
   $ sudo make install
   $ cd ..
   $ ln -sf $PWD/cl-meld.asd ~/quicklisp/local-projects/

- Compile and run programs

   Go to 'meld', the virtual machine directory, and read the README file.
